{"tid":2390701,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"光之美少女最新作 反派向主角求救 得到史無前例既答覆","createTime":"2021-02-01T17:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T18:09:28.000Z","uid":8307,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cb79ee44bd78d92e33b2c2b35d5b544733c9b1f1","tid":2390701,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:36:14.000Z","msg":"原文:<a href=\"http://jin115.com/archives/52311420.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjin115.com%2Farchives%2F52311420.html&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=46ad8104\" target=\"_blank\">http://jin115.com/archives/52311420.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EtBI_jcUcAUISdV?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEtBI_jcUcAUISdV%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=aae81a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反派求救<br />\n粉紅色隻野拉比林問主角 <br />\n我知道你好善良,但係救左條友又會同佢地有衝突<br />\n主角話其實佢唔想救<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EtBJDd8UwAUPHJh?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEtBJDd8UwAUPHJh%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=a766de51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉比林立即勁高興話 咁就唔好救,根本冇義務去救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果邊鳩個走出黎屌柒主角,會一拳打撚死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後成班勁開心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EtBLDclUUAATjhn?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEtBLDclUUAATjhn%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=03aba403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後面反派又再一次求救<br />\n主角立即嘴炮佢,話幫完佢只係比佢利用<br />\n<br />\n開完大技打柒左個反派之後,個反派比其他反派吸收左<br />\n成班o哂嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0aa3a10dae5784f427d23934f014687954a20b","tid":2390701,"uid":33651,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"好點暗<br />\n個主角唔幫人<br />\n人地可能真係想改邪歸正<br />\n諗起反共班人，成日一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n光之美少女正正反映左香港社會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4862789ebbd7b31d0a83d4457ab9c7445c393d","tid":2390701,"uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"講漏左少少<br />\n一開波成班仲要係到扮sad<br />\n之後一決定唔幫手,立即勁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n詳細睇返最新個套光之美少女 第42集"},{"pid":"0e24f9341d4c088b3ae64ee5c9ecc4102261c550","tid":2390701,"uid":8307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"de0aa3a10dae5784f427d23934f014687954a20b","tid":2390701,"uid":33651,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"好點暗<br />\n個主角唔幫人<br />\n人地可能真係想改邪歸正<br />\n諗起反共班人，成日一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n光之美少女正正反映左香港社會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:44:03.000Z","msg":"唔講利弊<br />\n光之美少女應該係提倡好正面既價值觀<br />\n可能佢想教人唔好比人利用個善心<br />\n但係咁樣教人猜忌其他人唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a99245e21a340d79b54ff81fabc3e63a71d186f","tid":2390701,"uid":16567,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"大個女要知人間險惡<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係會比支那人害死<br />\n<br />\n信支那人會改邪歸正？"},{"pid":"d18a5dce30b6b3206b741e33752f92513135e849","tid":2390701,"uid":188282,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"de0aa3a10dae5784f427d23934f014687954a20b","tid":2390701,"uid":33651,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"好點暗<br />\n個主角唔幫人<br />\n人地可能真係想改邪歸正<br />\n諗起反共班人，成日一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n光之美少女正正反映左香港社會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/ra